# Curated left-sidebar for the "Quick start" (notes) vault.
#
# Replaces the auto [navigation] tree (which sorts alphabetically by title and
# so ignores the 1-/2-/3- section prefixes) with the intended reading order.
# Format mirrors nav.nav:  "Label" : "target"   (children prefixed with `-`,
# depth 1). Targets are vault-relative; each section links to its index page.
#
# Maintained by hand: a new page must be added here to appear in the sidebar.

"Quick start" : "@notes/"

